Monitor Compliance

Description: Monitor website compliance with GDPR regulations and user privacy.

Goals:

   - Ensure ongoing compliance with GDPR regulations.
   - Protect user privacy through regular monitoring and updates.

Scope: This initiative will involve regularly monitoring the website's compliance with GDPR regulations and user privacy through audits and updates as needed.

Outcomes:

   - Continued compliance with GDPR regulations.
   - Ongoing protection of user privacy.

Deliverables:

   - Regular compliance audits.
   - Updated data collection and usage practices as needed.

Milestones:

   - Compliance audit completed (Quarterly).
   - Data collection and usage practices updated as needed (Quarterly).

Constraints: Limited resources for compliance monitoring and updates.

Assumptions: User privacy regulations will not significantly change.

Risks:

   - Non-compliance with GDPR regulations.
   - User mistrust and reduced engagement due to privacy concerns.

Dependencies: None.

Team: Legal Counsel (Lead), Data Analyst, Web Developer, Project Manager.


